{"abstract": "Mr. Hottelet, only 26 when he was hired by Edward R. Murrow, covered the invasion of Normandy and the Battle of the Bulge for CBS News.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/18/business/media/richard-c-hottelet-is-dead-at-97-cbs-correspondent-was-last-of-the-murrow-boys.html", "snippet": "Mr. Hottelet, only 26 when he was hired by Edward R. Murrow, covered the invasion of Normandy and the Battle of the Bulge for CBS News.", "lead_paragraph": "Richard C. Hottelet, who covered the D-Day invasion of Normandy and the Battle of the Bulge for CBS and became the last survivor of the \u201cMurrow Boys,\u201d the network\u2019s pioneering World War II radio newsmen who worked under Edward R. Murrow, died on Wednesday at his home in Wilton, Conn. He was 97. ", "print_section": "A", "print_page": "37", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/18/business/18hottelet-pic2/18hottelet-pic2-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 494, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/12/18/business/18hottelet-pic2/18hottelet-pic2-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 494}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/18/business/18hottelet-pic2/18hottelet-pic2-jumbo.jpg", "height": 842, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/18/business/18hottelet-pic2/18hottelet-pic2-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1420, "width": 1726, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/12/18/business/18hottelet-pic2/18hottelet-pic2-thumbStandard-v2.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumb